  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onions and cook until they are translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for an additional minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the red curry paste and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let cook for 5 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the fish sauce, lime juice, and soy sauce.",
    "Add the bean sprouts and cook until they are tender, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Cook the rice noodles according to the package instructions and set aside.",
    "To assemble the dish, place a portion of the noodles onto a plate and top with the curry sauce and garnish with cilantro."
